    <title>All you need is a home</title>
    <sections>
      <section>
        <title>China's ghost cities</title>
        <abstract>In the past 20 years China has constructed hundreds of new cities and districts.
        </abstract>
        <chapter>
          <title>New ones</title>
            <paragraph>
              <list type="unordered">
                <item>Caused by the urbanization boom</item>
                <item>Under-populated places</item>
                <item>Mostly unknown places</item>
                <item>In the north of the country</item>
                <item>New industries try to develop</item>
              </list>
            </paragraph>
          </chapter>
          <chapter>
            <title>Past ones</title>
            <paragraph>
              <list type="unordered">
                <item>Now filled up with people</item>
                <item>They become economical engines</item>
                <item>Located near big cities</item>
              </list>
            </paragraph>
          </chapter>
