        </section>
        <section>
          <title>Houses in China</title>
          <subtitle>Some data</subtitle>
          <chapter>
            <paragraph>
              <list type="unordered">
                <item>90% families which own their home</item>
                <item>N°5 in world’s list of countries by home ownership rate</item>
                <item>25-30 years: average lifetime of a house in China</item>
                <item>80% own it outright, with no mortgage or loans</item>
                <item>20% urban household with more than one house</item>
                <item>7 of the most expensive cities in the world are based in China</item>
              </list>
            </paragraph>
          </chapter>
          <keywords>
            <keyword name="Southeastern Asia"/>
