          <title>55% Investment funds and SOCIMIs*</title>
          <paragraph>They have increased their market share to become one of the main players, driving the market in the process.
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph>*SOCIMIs or REIT: SOCIMI (sociedades cotizadas de inversión en el mercado inmobiliario) also known as REIT (real estate investment trust) is a company that owns, and in most cases operates, income-producing real estate.
          </paragraph>
        </chapter>
